OL,7,FA former carer in Guernsey who
OL,8,Fdefrauded vulnerable clients and
OL,9,Ffriends of hundreds of thousands of
OL,10,Fpounds has been sentenced to four and
OL,11,Fa half years in prison.
OL,13,FBiljana Zekavica defrauded her five
OL,14,Fvictims of almost #200,000 by telling
OL,15,Fthem she needed money for a range of
OL,16,Fprojects, including home renovations,
OL,17,Fmedical procedures, and business
OL,18,Fprojects.
