OL,7,FMany of these stories were fabricated,
OL,8,Fand the majority of the money was
OL,9,Fnever repaid.
OL,11,FThe court heard how Zekavica's actions
OL,12,Fhad a significant impact on her
OL,13,Fvictims' lives.
OL,15,FChris Bale, a friend of Zekavica's,
OL,16,Fwaived his right to anonymity to tell
OL,17,Fthe court how he loaned her #10,000 to
OL,18,Fhelp buy equipment to start a cleaning
OL,19,Fbusiness.
