OL,7,FHe told ITV Channel that once he found
OL,8,Fout the sums other victims had lost,
OL,9,Fhe felt his situation "paled in
OL,10,Fcomparison".
OL,12,FHe continues: "People have lost
OL,13,Fgenerational wealth, inheritance,
OL,14,Fthings that would have put children
OL,15,Fthrough college, things that would
OL,16,Fhave helped them, and a deposit for a
OL,17,Fhouse.
OL,19,F"We're not in that boat - so, we'll be
OL,20,Fokay."
