OL,7,FTwo of Zekavica's other victims have
OL,8,Fsince died.
OL,10,FOne 89-year-old man who employed her
OL,11,Fas a cleaner was defrauded of almost
OL,12,F#80,000.
OL,14,FThe wife of another man, who loaned
OL,15,FZekavica #35,000 to assist with house
OL,16,Frepairs, asked for repayment to help
OL,17,Ffund her daughter's return to the
OL,18,Fisland to scatter his ashes.
OL,20,FThis money never materialised.
