OL,7,FThe victim impact statement of a man
OL,8,Fin his 90s who was ultimately left
OL,9,Fwith less than #60 after lending
OL,10,FZekavica money repeatedly over three
OL,11,Fyears was also heard by the court.
OL,13,FIt read: "At the time I believed I was
OL,14,Fhelping someone I trusted, my carer -
OL,15,FI relied on her, and she abused the
OL,16,Ftrust I had in her.
OL,18,F"To take advantage of an elderly man
OL,19,Funder the guise of care is a
OL,20,Fdetestable act."
