OL,7,FShe added: "You took advantage of your
OL,8,Fposition as a long-term carer to some
OL,9,Fof your victims, and the impact for
OL,10,Fsome was at the highest level of
OL,11,Fseriousness".
OL,13,FSentencing was run consecutively for
OL,14,Feach of the five victims.
OL,16,FAn application will be made for a
OL,17,Fconfiscation order in respect of the
OL,18,F#207,000 that's yet to be paid.
